skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: server status
des: This application asks the Field Intelligence Laboratory's computer if it is online and available for remote connections. It is used to allow students and faculty to determine that the server is properly configured and available for use without having to open a remote desktop connection for validation.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
